commit message:
Add build targets and remove now missing thing from imports

Signed-off-by: Jonas Kalderstam <jonas@kalderstam.se>

Created free version

Free version lacks dropbox and location reminders. Gtask sync
still works.

To build the free version, one needs to do:

./gradlew installFreeDebug

versus the non free versions:

./gradlew installPlayDebug
./gradlew installPlayBetaDebug

fixes #269
